"Blessed"
is the word i feel while watching this video 😇

My twin pregnancy journey was not so smooth.... It was a rollercoaster ride, i must say.... But with the help of my beautiful & caring family and the support of my friends like family, we finally got our two little munchkins 👨‍👩‍👦‍👦 Vriha 👧and Vidhaansh 👦

Thank you God for blessing us and being on our side all the time 🙏🏻🙏🏻🧿🧿

latestPosts.caption:
Two little ones who brighten up our lives with their smiles and tiny steps...❤️🌟🧿

To see them grow little by little...day after day is joy in itself... We really can't believe that our tiny little twins have become one year old 🥺🥺 05.04.2023

The love, the blessings and the wishes they recieve by just being here is so fulfilling to see...

Ohh how we love you Vrihu & Vidhu... Ohh we love you so so much our darlings...👨‍👩‍👧‍👦🫶

How the time flies by and we find ourselves to see you turn 1, you little ones of ours...

Hope you are always blessed, oh so blessed dear ones of ours...

Happiest happiest Birthday Dearest Vrihu & Vidhu...🎂🥳🧁...

Stay blessed 🤗🤗

We love you so so so much 😘😘🫶🫶🫰🫰
